==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Smicker
<hw>Smick"er</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>smicere</ets> tasteful,
trim. See <er>Smicker</er>, <pos>v.</pos>]</ety> <def>Amorous; wanton;
gay; spruce.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Smickering</ent>⟦br⟧
